snippet.title: Lethal Company - SCP Facility mod WIP
snippet.description:
A WIP mod adding the SCP facility from SCP:Containment Breach as a dungeon, currently found as an uncommon variant on Titan.

Obviously there's still some minor issues such as a lack of room variety, the overly large size of the facility, and some lighting bugs, but it's otherwise working pretty well. I'm trying to have this ready by this weekend for an alpha release.
